    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep luster without a single chip, scratch, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive care. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
